anek Czecks In|url=http://www.evertonfc.com/news/archive/2014/01/31/stanek-czechs-in|work=evertonfc.com|publisher=Everton FC|date=31 January 2014|accessdate=2 February 2014}}</ref>\n|}\n{{col-2}}\n\n=== Out ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Player\n! To\n! Date\n! Fee\n! class=unsortable | Ref.\n|-\n| {{sort|Bidwell, Jake|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Jake Bidwell]]}}\n| {{sort|Brentford|{{Flagicon|ENG}} [[Brentford F.C.|Brentford]]}}\n| 17 June 2013\n| Undisclosed (~\u00a31m)\n| align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite news |title=Bidwell Joins Bees |url=http://www.evertonfc.com/news/archive/2013/06/17/bidwell-joins-bees |work=evertonfc.com |publisher=Everton FC |date=17 June 2013 |accessdate=17 June 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130620154554/http://www.evertonfc.com/news/archive/2013/06/17/bidwell-joins-bees |archive-date=20 June 2013 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n| {{sort|Hammar, Johan|{{flagicon|SWE}} Johan Hammar}}\n| {{sort|Malm\u00f6 FF|{{Flagicon|SWE}} [[Malm\u00f6 FF]]}}\n| 18 June 2013\n| Free\n| align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite news|title=Malm\u00f6 FF skriver kontrakt med Johan Hammar |url=http://www.mff.se/Aktuellt/Nyheter/2013-06-18_Hammar_skirver_kontrakt_med_MFF |work=mff.se |publisher=Malm\u00f6 FF |date=18 June 2013 |accessdate=1 July 2013 |language=Swedish |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130624035554/http://www.mff.se/Aktuellt/Nyheter/2013-06-18_Hammar_skirver_kontrakt_med_MFF |archivedate=24 June 2013 }}</ref><ref name=\"released\" />\n|-\n| {{sort|Hitzlsperger, Thomas|{{flagicon|GER}} [[Thomas Hitzlsperger]]}}\n| ''Released''\n| 1 July 2013\n| Free\n| align=\"center\"|<ref name=\"released\">{{cite news |title=Three Deals To Expire |url=http://www.evertonfc.com/news/archive/2013/06/05/three-deals-to-expire |work=evertonfc.com |publisher=Everton FC |date=6 June 2013 |accessdate=2 July 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130710074933/http://www.evertonfc.com/news/archive/2013/06/05/three-deals-to-expire |archive