tonfc.com/news/archive/2013/09/13/garbutt-loaned-to-colchester |archive-date=2 April 2015 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Garbutt Recalled |url=http://www.evertonfc.com/news/archive/2014/01/28/garbutt-recalled |work=evertonfc.com |publisher=Everton FC |date=28 January 2014 |accessdate=29 January 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{sort|Duffy, Shane|{{flagicon|IRL}} [[Shane Duffy]]}}\n| {{sort|Yeovil Town|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Yeovil Town F.C.|Yeovil Town]]}}\n| 26 September 2013\n| End of season\n| align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite news |title=Shane Duffy: Everton defender joins Yeovil Town on loan |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24291069 |work=BBC Sport|publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=26 September 2013 |accessdate=28 September 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Duffy To Stay With Yeovil |url=http://www.evertonfc.com/news/archive/2013/12/27/duffy-to-stay-with-yeovil |work=evertonfc.com |publisher=Everton FC |date=27 December 2013 |accessdate=28 December 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{sort|Lundstram, John|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[John Lundstram]]}}\n| {{sort|Yeovil Town|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Yeovil Town F.C.|Yeovil Town]]}}\n| 28 November 2013\n| 10 March 2014<ref group=\"n\">Loan was originally scheduled until the end of the season, but was ended early.</ref>\n| align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite news |title=Lundstram Heads To Yeovil |url=http://www.evertonfc.com/news/archive/2013/11/28/lundstram-heads-to-yeovil |work=evertonfc.com |publisher=Everton FC |date=28 November 2013 |accessdate=10 December 2013}}</ref><ref name=\"young trio\">{{cite news |title=Young Trio Loaned Out |url=http://www.evertonfc.com/news/archive/2014/01/01/young-trio-loaned-out |work=evertonfc.com |publisher=Everton FC |date=1 January 2014 |accessdate=2 January 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Lundstram Recalled From Yeovil |url=http://www.evertonfc.com/news/archive/2014/03/10/lundstram-recalled-from-yeovil |work=evertonfc.com |publisher=Everton FC |date=10 March 2014 |accessdate=5 April 2